  "text": "Even more important, apparently no genetic information is available for the Sumatra population of the Javan rhinoceros, while in contrast DNA sequence fragments of the 12S rRNA and the non-coding D-loop are available from specimens from the highly endangered West Java population as well as from the now extinct populations in Vietnam [CITATION_1] .",
